Nanette Bordeaux https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanette_Bordeaux 0 Nanette Bordeaux (April 3, 1911 – September 20, 1956) was a French Canadian-born American film actress. Born Hélène Olivine Veilleux, Bordeaux made over 15 film appearances between 1942 and 1957.
